(467, 111, 1, 'ACC-J2|Taxable Goods|Glazed Round Ginger Jar with Lid|none|A pretty blue & white ceramic jar with lid. Painted with one form of traditional Chinese lotus scroll decoration in cobalt blue this beautiful jar could make an attractive ornament or a pretty flower vase.|150|1'),
(446, 112, 1, 'ACC-J3|Taxable Goods|Blue & White Temple Jar with Double Happiness Symbol|none|An elegant temple jar made from Chinese ceramic. Lacquered in white with traditional blue Chinese decorative patterns and double happiness symbol. Temple jars are very ornate and make an impressive feature in any rooms. Temple jars could also make practical uses as a grand storage vessels. A perfect wedding present with symbolic meanings.|200|1'),
(443, 59, 1, 'Lu-059|Taxable Goods|Antique Blue Lacquer table with a Drawer c.1920 Gansu Province|none|A charateristic blue lacquer small table beautifully restored to retain tits period design features. Full of character and charm with a blue glossy lacquer finish, a brass handled drawer, and handcurved detail on the base apron these solid wood table could make a charactful bedside table, a playroom stool, or a small hallway display stand.|300|1'),
(444, 110, 1, 'ACC-J1|Taxable Goods|Glazed Round Ginger Jar with Lid|none|A pretty blue & white ceramic jar with lid. Painted with traditional Chinese lotus scroll decoration in cobalt blue this beautiful jar could make an attractive ornament or a pretty flower vase.|150|1'),
(441, 57, 1, 'Lu-057|Taxable Goods|Vintage Blue Lacquer 2 Drawers Low Table c.1950|none|A charming vintage table with a glossy blue lacquer finish. Beautifully reclaimed with decorative brass hardware, trunky square legs and traditional turned in feet his charming vintage table will make an eye-catching hallway piece, a playroom bench, or a cloarkroom stand.|410|1'),
(442, 58, 1, 'Lu-058|Taxable Goods|Antique Green Lacquer 3 Drawers Table c.1920 Shangdong Province|none|An antique ornate low table with butterfly shaped decorative features dated c.1920 from Shandong Province. Full of charcter and charm, with a touch of green lacquer finish, decorative brass handles and beatifully handcarved sides, this antique low table could make a stunning hallway bench, a playroom bench, or a cloarkroom stand.|870|1'),
(440, 56, 1, 'Lu-056|Taxable Goods|Disdressed Blue Lacquered Bench|none|A lovely blue lacquered bench with curved spandrels and charming oriental turned in feet. A fabulous solution to busy dinning for children and families. This gorgeous bench stores away neatly under the matching blue lacquered dining table and provides seating for as many can squeeze on. You could use it on its own in a hallway, landing, drawing room or as a end of bed bench.|1100|1'),
(439, 55, 1, 'Lu-055|Taxable Goods|Antique Lacquered 3 door Wood Cabinet with Handpainted Scenes c.1920 Gansu Province|none|A truly evocative and picturesque antique sideboard handcrafted c.1920 depicting poetic Chinese rural Scenes. Dated c.1920 carefully restored this beautifully crafted oriental cabinet houses a dark green lacquered wooden interior recess, three cupboards, removable doors and internal shelves. This antique solid wooden sideboard will enhance any home interioor with its rich surface and texture details. It cleverly works as living room storage, hallway storage or funky kitchen storage.|1920|1'),
(436, 52, 1, 'Lu-052|Taxable Goods|Vintage Blue Grey Lacquered Rice Measure c.1950|none|This lovely distreed blue grey wooden rice measure have originally been used by merchandiser to measure the quantity of rice to be sold. This vintage wooden rice measure would make very attractive storage for bedlines, bathroom towers, toddlers toys or newspapers. With so many uses, very household needs one!|120|1'),
(437, 53, 1, 'Lu-053|Taxable Goods|Antique Dark Blue Lacquer Bench with Decorative Details c.1920|none|Anitque lacquered bench beautifully crafted in to decorative details with charming Oriental turned in feet. Dated c.1920 elegantly restored this dark blue lacquered bench is suitable as dinng seating or an occational seat|270|1'),
(438, 54, 1, 'Lu-054|Taxable Goods|Distressed Cream Lacquered Small Cabinet|none|A pair of decoratedsmall cabinet beautifully crafted to retain the periods design features. These solid wood cabinets are full of character and charm, with a dark cream glossy lacquer finish. Each with removable tops, solid legs and hand-painted decorative front. These small cabinets will effortlessly add any home storage with an oriental touch, work cleverly as bedside table, toy storage, or end of bed storage bench|320|1'),
(434, 50, 1, 'Lu-050|Taxable Goods|Glazed Dark Blue Ceramic stool|none|This eautifully glazed dark blue ceramic stool would make a lovely side table, occational tale or a very decorative drawing room piece.|190|1'),
(435, 51, 1, 'Lu-051|Taxable Goods|Blue Lacquer Day Bed|none|A beautifully handcrafted bed with glossay blue lacquer finish. Carefully applied a touch of blue lacquer allows the original wooden coulor shimmering through. This stunning bed could make a charming daybed, or a child''s bed.|910|1'),
(432, 48, 1, 'Lu-048|Taxable Goods|Dark Grey Lacquer 3 Drawers Table|none|A dark grey 3 drawers table has an eye-catching distressed look. Full of charcter and charm, with a glossy dark grey lacquer finish, decorative iron hardware, and sqare legs this gorgeous table will effortlessly add a touch of oriental charm to any hallway, drawing room, or bedroom.|820|1'),
(431, 47, 1, 'Lu-047|Taxable Goods|Antique Blue Handpainted Lacquer 2 doors Cabinet c.1930 Gansu Province|none|A striking blue lacquer antique cabinet from the Gansu province of China dated c.1930. Beasutifully resored, this solid wood cabinet has two doors and an eye-catching distressed look. With a dominant blue look this piece also has a multitude of other colours within it showing the layers of history through its crackle glaze lacquer. Full of character and charm, with a deep cupboard, original handpainted decorative doors and solid legs this piece of anique cabinet will efforlessly add a touch of colour and interesting history to any space of interior design.|1190|1'),
(433, 49, 1, 'Lu-049|Taxable Goods|Vintage Mellow Wedding Cabinet c.1930 Shanxi Province|none|Majestic and beautifully elegant lacquered Chinese wedding cabinet c.1930 Shanxi Province. This exceptional Oriental coffer has the brass circular togetherness panel as the centre piece, creating an elegant contrast to the rectangular form of the cabinet. With two tall shelves, removable doors and a secret recess in the base of the cabinet, this splendid amoire would enhance any contemporary interior as versatile storage|1280|1'),
(428, 44, 1, 'Lu-044|Taxable Goods|Blue Lacquer Round Table|none|A pleasingly curvaceous round table with detaled stand. Full of character and charm, with a cracled glaze blue, green and brown lacquer finish and stunning durable surface this table is a comnination of function and sculptual beauty. This gorgeous table could make a great small dining or an eye-catching occational table.|1460|1'),
(429, 45, 1, 'Lu-045|Taxable Goods|Distressed Llight Blue Dining Table|none|A stunning solid wooden table with gorgeous disdressed looking. A traditional Chinese craftman techniques have been used for joints of all the parts of the table with elegantly curved decorative panels around legs. A humbling distressed look of this dinning table will add an understated elegance to any dinning room.|1600|1'),
(426, 42, 1, 'Lu-042|Taxable Goods|Antique Light Blue Lacquer 2 doors 3 drawers Low Cabinet c.1920 Dongbei Province|none|An antique baby blue lacquered low cabinet with 2 doors and 3 drawers dated c.1930 from Dongbei Province. Full of character and charm, beautifully restored with a touch of light blue glossay lacquer to allow original wooden courlors shimmering through, this characteristic low cabinet would make a fantastic hallway bench with planty of storage/organiser space, a charming cloakroom shoe stand, or a playroom bench.|410|1'),
(430, 46, 1, 'Lu-046|Taxable Goods|Antique Disdressed Blue Lacquered Table c.1900 Shanxi Province|none|Antique blue lacquered table with oval top, square legs and beautifully sculptured lower shelf. This table will make a lovely stand along feature in any rooms. Dated back c.1900 elegantly restored this blue lacquered table would make a statement stand to display an ornate, a vase, or something special just for you|590|1'),
(427, 43, 1, 'Lu-043|Taxable Goods|Disdressed Round Stool|none|A wooden stool with a soft deged circular seat originated in Beijing. Beautifully hand crafted in Chinese pine wood with four square shaped legs and crossbar strtcher detail. This worker''s stool was made using traditional Oriental mortise and tenon joinery and has been finished with a blue distressed lacquer.|160|1'),
(423, 39, 1, 'Lu-039|Taxable Goods|Vintage Blue Lacquer Classic Coat Stand c.1950|none|This blue lacquer classic coat stand is a treasure found from 1950''s Beijing China. Beautifully made from Chines pine wood with hand-turned coat hooks and elegantly curved legs.|460|1'),
(424, 40, 1, 'Lu-040|Taxable Goods|Antique 2 Doors 4 Drawers low Cabinet c.1930 Gansu Province|none|An antique grey lacquer low cabinet with 2 doors and 4 drawers dated c.1930 from Gansu Province. Full of character and charm, carfully restored with grey glossy lacquer and decorative brass handles this humble low cabinet adds understated elegance to any interior settings. This charming low cabinet could be used as hallway bench, a cloak room storage, or an end of bed bench.|1020|1'),
(425, 41, 1, 'Lu-041|Taxable Goods|Antique Grey Lacquer Table with Carving Top c.1930 Gansu Province|none|A beautiful ornamental square dinning table with grey lacquer finish dating back c.1930 from Gansu Province. With straight legs, top detailing and stunningly hand carved decorative top this antique table will add a touch of oriental element to any charming kitchen or dining room. A see-through glass top and a single shelf add a practicality to this gorgeous piece.|910|1'),
(422, 38, 1, 'Lu-038|Taxable Goods|Antique Emerald Green Lacquer Console Table c.1900 Shanxi Province|none|An antique emerald lacquer console table dated c.1900 from the Shanxi Province. Beautifully restored with emerald green finish, decorative carved details, slender legs and traditional turned in feet this charming console table will effortlessly transform any hallway with a touch of beautiful corlor.|590|1'),
(420, 36, 1, 'Lu-036|Taxable Goods|Anique Dark Green 2 doors Cabinet c.1930 Gansu Province|none|A dark green lacquer distressed antique oriental cabinet dating abck to 1930 originating in Gansu province China. Full of character and charm with rich variaty of colours, glaze lacquer finishing, and beautifully carved decorative frames on the door, this dark green lacqured wooden caninet will make for charming dining room storage, living room stroage or a bedside table|910|1'),
(421, 37, 1, 'Lu-037|Taxable Goods|Vintage Blue Lacquer Oriental Alter Table c.1960|none|There are traces of the original blue lacquer still adorninig the beautiful natural wooden brown of this Chinese Altar Table with dates back to c.1950 from Shandong Province. Beautifully built with elm and elegant carveing details this alter table will make a statement hallway table or a long console for a touch of oriental element.|1320|1'),
(418, 34, 1, 'Lu-034|Taxable Goods|Antique Distressed Blue Lacque rCabinet c.1920 Gansu Province|none|A blue lacquered distressed antique oriental cabinet dating abck to 1920 originating in Gansu province China. This Chinese pine cabinet has a shabby chic blue lacquer finish on the doors and the frame. This blue lacqured wooden caninet will make for charming dining room storage, living room stroage or a bedside table|820|1'),
(419, 35, 1, 'Lu-035|Taxable Goods|Vintage Green Lacquer Wooden Desk c.1950|none|Perfect for a home study, this stylish and practical desk has 6 draws and a cabinet on each side. Originally used as a office table for two people to seat face to face. Dated c.1950 carefully restored this glossy lacquered desk will add unique feature to your stylish home study.|1640|1'),
(415, 31, 1, 'Lu-031|Taxable Goods|Antique Blue Lacquer Small Curved Table c.1900 Shanxi Province|none|A beautiful antique blue lacquer curved table dating backc.1900 from Shanxi Province. Full of charm and beautiful craftmanship with curved edge and decorative legs this small table will cleverly make for a charming coffee table, a child''s stool, or even a stand for any central piece of a dinning table.|300|1'),
(416, 32, 1, 'Lu-032|Taxable Goods|Handpainted 2 door Chinese Sideboard|none|This green lacquered oriental sideboard origniated in Beijing. The double cupboard houses a removable shelf and the two doors are decorated with handpainted oriental floral illustration. This beautiful sideboard cleverly works as a dining room storage , a useful wooden cupboard for a toy-room or colourful bedroom storage.|1100|1'),
(417, 33, 1, 'Lu-033|Taxable Goods|Antique Cream Lacquer Trunk c.1920 Shandong Province|none|An antique cream lacquered trunk decorated with a trace of original floral paint. This large wooden trund features a simple brass lock and carved details around the base. A magnificent storage solutions for elegant intriors.|270|1'),
(413, 29, 1, 'Lu-029|Taxable Goods|Antique Distressed Blue Lacquer Cabinet c.1920 Gansu Province|none|A blue lacquered distressed antique oriental cabinet dating abck to 1920 originating in Gansu province China. This Chinese pine cabinet has a shabby chic blue lacquer finish on the doors and the frame. This blue lacqured wooden caninet will make for charming dining room storage, living room stroage or a bedside table|780|1'),
(414, 30, 1, 'Lu-030|Taxable Goods|Antique Blue Lacquer Carved Table c.1900 Shanxi Province|none|A beautiful ornamental square dinning table with blue lacquer finish dating back c.1900 from Shanxi Province. With straight legs, top detailing and decorative corner carvings this antique table will add a touch of oriental element to any charming kitchen or dining room.|1370|1'),
(410, 26, 1, 'Lu-026|Taxable Goods|Dark Green/Brown Lacquer 3 doors Low Cabinet|none|This dark green/brown lacquered oriental low sideboard origniated in Beijing. The cupboard houses a removable shelf and the three doors are decorated with handpainted oriental floral illustration. This beautiful sideboard cleverly works as a dining room storage , a useful wooden cupboard for a toy-room, a wonderful bedroom storage or even a gorgeous cloakroom shoe cabinets|1000|1'),
(411, 27, 1, 'Lu-027|Taxable Goods|Pair of Grey Lacquer Small 2 Door Cabinet|none|A pair of grey lacquer small cabinet beautifully crafted to retain the periods design features. These solid wood cabinets are full of character and charm with a grey glossy lacquer finish. Each with 2 doors, hand-cured apron, and decorative brass hardware. These small cabinets will effortlessly add any home storage with an oriental touch, work cleverly as bedside table, toy storage, or child''s tools|370|1'),
(412, 28, 1, 'Lu-028|Taxable Goods|Cream Lacquer 4 doors 2 drawers Cabinet|none|A majestic and beautifully elegant lacquered cabinet with skillfully handpainted floral scenes . This exceptional oriental coffer has a circular togetherness pattern as the centre piece, creating an elegant contrast to the rectangular form of the cabinet. With 4 doors, removable shelves and 2 drawers in the middle of the cabinet, this splendid oriental amoire would enhance any contemporary interior as versatile storage.|1100|1'),
(409, 25, 1, 'Lu-025|Taxable Goods|Antique Green Lacquer 3 Drawers Console Table c.1930 Gansu|none|An antique green lacquer 3 drawers console table has an eye-catching distressed glossylook dating back c.1930 from Gansu Province. Full of charcter and charm, with layers of coulors shimmering through a green lacquer finish, decorative iron hardware, and sqare legs this gorgeous console table will effortlessly add a touch of oriental charm to any hallway.|870|1'),
(408, 24, 1, 'Lu-024|Taxable Goods|Vintage Blue Lacquer 5 drawers low Table c.1960|none|A gorgeous blue lacquer low table with five drawers, solid legs and traditional turned in feet. Carefully restored with a touch of blue lacquer to allow original green, yellow, brown colours shimering through the glazed surface this low cabinet will make a eye-catch dining room bench with storage, a hallway bench with organiser, or a children''s room table for all the siblings to share.|1280|1'),
(406, 22, 1, 'Lu-022|Taxable Goods|Red Lacquer 4 doors 4 drawers Cabinet|none|A gorgeous red lacquered oriental sideboard with 4 doors and 4 drawers. The cupboard houses a removable shelf and the four doors are decorated with handpainted oriental floral illustration. This beautiful sideboard cleverly works as a dining room storage , a statement drawing room sideboard, or a stunning hallway piece.|1230|1'),
(407, 23, 1, 'Lu-023|Taxable Goods|Pair of Grey Lacquer Square Tables|none|A pair of grey lacquer table with an eye-catching distressed look. Full of charcter and charm with a glaze grey lacquer finish, hardwearing rattan table tops, slender tapered legs and traditional turned in feet these tables will make a lovely stand along feature in any rooms, and would make a statement stand to display an ornate, a vase, or something special just for you.|340|1'),
(405, 21, 1, 'Lu-021|Taxable Goods|Antique Blue Lacquer 6 Drawers Table c.1900 Shandong Province|none|An antique blue lacquer 6 drawers long table with low shelf dating back c.1900 from Shandong Province. Carefully restored with elegant drawer starage and delicate brass tab handles. Full of character and charm this long table will make a wonderful statement hallway consle table, a sofa table, or a dining room sidetable. Low shelf is perfect for any statement display.|1830|1'),
(404, 20, 1, 'Lu-020|Taxable Goods|Antique Light Green Lacquered Bucket c.1920 Shanxi Province|none|This traditional Chinesestorage bucket is an aged antique, dates back to c.1920 is from Shanxi Province. This beautiful display piece has been carfully restored and finished in a light green lacquer. It was hand made in Chinese pine wood, with an round shaped bottem and a gently curved lid. This attractive bucket will make unusual decorative items or functional storage solutions, and is an easy way to add some oriental touchs to any room of any interior design.|220|1'),
(403, 19, 1, 'Lu-019|Taxable Goods|Antique Distressed Lacquered 3 doors Cabinet c. 1930 Gansu Province|none|A solidly buitl rustic Chinese antique sideboard carefully restored with a rich blue, grey and brown crakled distressed look, finished with durable coats of lacquer. Crafted in the Gansu Province, Nortwest China c.1930. This Chinese antique cabinet featurres four doors, with four cupboards featuring handcrafted shelved recess. Adorned with brass leaf tab and plates, this elegant solid Oriental cupboard has been exquisitely crafted to beautiful finish. This anique Chinese sideboard would look impressive in wither traditional home or ultra modern apartment. Suitable as large bedroom storage, a statment drawing room or hallway peice.|1640|1'),
(402, 18, 1, 'Lu-018|Taxable Goods|Antique Light Green Lacquered Large Bucket c.1920 Shanxi Province|none|This traditional Chinese cloth-washing bucket is an aged antique, dates back to c.1920 is from Shanxi Province. This beautiful display piece has been carfully restored and finished in a light green lacquer. It was hand made in Chinese pine wood, with an round shaped bottem and a gently curved lid. This attractive bucket will make unusual decorative items or functional storage solutions, and is an easy way to add some oriental touchs to any room of any interior design.|220|1'),
(398, 14, 1, 'Lu-014|Taxable Goods|Blue Lacquer Chinese Ancient Box c.1950|none|A characteristic Chinese ancient syle box with beautifully handcarved people and floral figure details. Carefully restored with light blue lacquer, elegantly curved handles and very charming ancient open mechanism, this stunning box would make a very attractive ornsment and an useful storage solution.|220|1'),
(393, 9, 1, 'Lu-009|Taxable Goods|Baby Blue Distressed Round stool|none|Round wooden stool beautifully hand crafted in Chinese pine wood with three legs and quirky strut detail. This worker''s stool has been made using traditional Oriental mortise and tenon, with a baby blue distressed lacquered finish. Exuding character and charm, this architectural stool would work well as a quirky addition to any interior, suitable kitchen stool, dining stool or dressing table stool.|160|1'),
(394, 10, 1, 'Lu-010|Taxable Goods|Dark Blue Floral stool|none|Floral shaped wooden stool beautifully hand crafted in Chinese pine wood with three legs and quirky strut detail. This beautiful stool has been made using traditional Oriental mortise and tenon, with a dark blue distressed lacquered finish. Exuding character and charm, this architectural stool would work well as a quirky addition to any interior, suitable kitchen stool, dining stool or dressing table stool.|160|1'),
(401, 17, 1, 'Lu-017|Taxable Goods|Antique Smokey Grey Lacquer Wooden Stool with Storage c.1900 Ningbo Province|none|Antique smokey grey lacquer wooden stool, originally used as rice barrel, could be used as a delightful sofa table as weell as a side table or an occational table. Dated c.1900 beautifully restored this wooden tool can also be used as a versatile storage or a charming linen basket.|160|1'),
