(399, 15, 1, 'Lu-015|Taxable Goods|Antique Blue Lacquer 2 Door Cabinet c.1900 Gansu Province|none|A striking blue lacquer antique cabinet from the Gansu province of China dated c.1900. Beasutifully resored, this solid wood cabinet has two doors and an eye-catching distressed look. With a dominant blue look this piece also has a multitude of other colours within it showing the layers of history through its crackle glaze lacquer. Full of character and charm, with a deep cupboard, original handpainted decorative doors and solid legs this piece of anique Chinese furniture will efforlessly add a touch of colour and history to any space of interior design.|780|1'),
(396, 12, 1, 'Lu-012|Taxable Goods|Anitque Grey Lacquer Console Table c.1920 Beijing Province|none|An antique grey lacquer console table dated c.1920 from the Beijing China. Beautifully restored with grey lacquer finish, decorative carved corners, and slender legs this charming console table will effortlessly transform any hallway with a touch of oriental element.|550|1'),
(397, 13, 1, 'Lu-013|Taxable Goods|Antique Distressed Blue Lacquer Cabinet c.1920 Gansu Province|none|A blue lacquered distressed antique oriental cabinet dating abck to 1920 originating in Gansu province China. This Chinese pine cabinet has a shabby chic blue lacquer finish on the doors and the frame. This blue lacqured wooden caninet will make for charming dining room storage, living room stroage or a bedside table|910|1'),
(395, 11, 1, 'Lu-011|Taxable Goods|Vintage Distressed Floral stool c.1950|none|Floral shaped wooden stool beautifully hand crafted in Chinese pine wood with three legs and quirky strut detail. This vintage stool has been made using traditional Oriental mortise and tenon, with a duck egg blue distressed lacquered finish. Exuding character and charm, this architectural stool would work well as a quirky addition to any interior, suitable kitchen stool, dining stool or dressing table stool.|160|1'),
(392, 8, 1, 'Lu-008|Taxable Goods|Vintage Blue Lacquer 3 drawers Table c.1950|none|A charming blue lacquer vintage table with original brown coloured surface. Beautifully reclaimed to retain many original features including vintage handles, elegrantly curved bars between square legs. This charming vintage table will make an eye-catching coffee table, or an interesting statement piece in any rooms.|640|1'),
