(388, 4, 1, 'Lu-004|Taxable Goods|Vintage Grey Lacquer 2 Drawers Table c.1950|none|A vintage grey lacquer 2 drawers table is a great treasure find from 1950''s Beijing China. Beautifully reclaimed with grey lacquer finish, decorative iron hardware, and slender legs this charming table could be used as a console table, or a dressing tablel effortlessly transform any room with a touch of oriental element.|550|1'),
