(73, 4, 72, 0, 37, 'none'),
(74, 4, 73, 0, 37, 'There are traces of the original blue lacquer still adorninig the beautiful natural wooden brown of this Chinese Altar Table with dates back to c.1950 from Shandong Province.     Beautifully built with elm and elegant carveing details this alter table will make a statement hallway table or a long console for a touch of oriental element.'),
(75, 4, 72, 0, 38, 'none'),
