(79, 4, 72, 0, 40, 'none'),
(80, 4, 73, 0, 40, 'An antique grey lacquer low cabinet with 2 doors and 4 drawers dated c.1930 from Gansu Province.     Full of character and charm, carfully restored with grey glossy lacquer and decorative brass handles this humble low cabinet adds understated elegance to any interior settings.     This charming low cabinet could be used as hallway bench, a cloak room storage, or an end of bed bench.'),
(81, 4, 72, 0, 41, 'none'),
